Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:51.89,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}迷い込んだ僕は僕に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:55.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}消え隠れていく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:42.16,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}感情的烈馬 一旦任之脫韁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:45.32,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}便再也找不到方向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:53.71,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}罪惡的扳機 本已沾染血光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:57.00,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}卻漸漸辨不清形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:02.80,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}若要將恨意驅趕出心房
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:08.39,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}還如何讓你把命償?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:14.27,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}掘塵封過往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:20.40,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}只為填罪業汪洋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:25.62,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}怨凜冽鋒芒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:32.29,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}頷首撫刻骨心傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:40.42,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}苦痛亦盡數遺忘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:43.97,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}身陷曲折迴廊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:51.89,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}既迷失原本模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:55.44,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}何不遁世韜光?
